README for pacupdate
=======================

Pacupdate is a small notifier for Arch Linux (pacman) updates.

Many thanks to the following people who directly and indirectly helped with this project:

    * Henrique C. Alves <hcarvalhoalves@gmail.com>
    * Og Maciel <ogmaciel@gnome.org>
    * Paulo Matias <matias@archlinux-br.org>

DEPENDENCIES
============

sudo
pygtk >= 2.10
python-notify
notification-daemon

INSTALLATION
============
See the 'INSTALL' file.
